						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone in the Basavaṇṇa temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged record belonging to the <hi rend="bold">17th century A.D.</hi> is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Rudhirōdgāri, Pushya ba. 14</hi> and records a grant made to a certain <hi rend="bold">Buḷḷappa,</hi> by <hi rend="bold">Basaṇṇa-Nāyaka,</hi> son of <hi rend="bold">Bommaṇṇa-Nāyaka of Naṟugunda.</hi> The details of the grant are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
